de: Contribution Agreement between the United Nations Office for Project Services (UNOPS) and the Government of the Swiss Confederation, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland (seco) concerning United Nations Trade Cluster Programme Tanzania  - 20-03-2014 - Vereinbarung zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und dem Büro der Vereinten Nationen für Projektdienste (UNOPS) betreffend die Schaffung eines Treuhandfonds zur Finanzierung eines technischen Assistenzprojektes in Tansania
en: Contribution Agreement between the United Nations Office for Project Services (UNOPS) and the Government of the Swiss Confederation, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland (seco) concerning United Nations Trade Cluster Programme Tanzania  - 20-03-2014 - Contribution Agreement between the United Nations Office for Project Services (UNOPS) and the Government of the Swiss Confederation, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland (seco) concerning United Nations Trade Cluster Programme Tanzania
fr: Contribution Agreement between the United Nations Office for Project Services (UNOPS) and the Government of the Swiss Confederation, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland (seco) concerning United Nations Trade Cluster Programme Tanzania  - 20-03-2014 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et le Bureau des Nations Unies des services d'appui aux projets (UNOPS) concernant l'établissement d'un fonds pour le financement d'un programme de coopération technique en Tanzanie
